The Midway
Executive Ticket
Book.
Midway
Airlines
It guarantees you today's
low fares. For a full year!
Ten tickets to whichever Midway
cities you choose -all good at
today's fares* for a full year.
And if you can't use all the tickets,
give them to friends or we'll
redeem them for the price
you paid.
For further information, write to:
Executive Ticket Books, Midway
Airlines, Inc., Midway Airport,
Chicago, IL 60638.
*excluding promotional fares
CHICAGO'S MIDWAY AIRPORT.
EASY TO GET TO,
EASY TO GET THROUGH.
It's right in the city, just 8 miles
from the Loop. You'll save time, cab
fare...even bus fare on airport
buses to major downtown hotels
and convention centers. And
you'll appreciate the uncrowded
concourses, speedy baggage
handling, and convenient
close-in parking.
PLEASE DON'T BE A NO-SHOW
An unexpected delay? A change of
plans? Whatever the reason you're
unable to use your Midway Airlines
reservations, please let us know.
